        "char_start": 609,
        "episode_id": "ep-bccfce5798a83a6e",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Honestly, Index funds are not a strategy \u2014 they're the absence of one. That's their advantage. We've seen this play out at teams using Morningstar. Most of the cost shows up downstream, which is why teams keep paying it.",
